<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="V" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Virtuously" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Virtuously,</orth> in a virtuous manner, in conformity with the moral law: <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.3.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. IV, 3, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.16" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.127" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 3, 127</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 1, 7</bibl>. <cit><quote>we are so v. bound,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 1.2.232" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 2, 232</bibl></cit> (== efficaciously? powerfully?).
